Post</source><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 05:14:19 +0800</pubDate><category>大模型</category><category>语音</category><category>TTS</category></item><item><title>Cursor 博客：Agent 集群与新型模型经济学</title><link>https://cursor.com/blog/agent-swarm-model-economics</link><description>Cursor 博客探讨 Agent 集群与新型模型经济学，认为多 Agent 协作将改变模型使用模式，降低推理成本。（来源：Cursor Blog）</description><guid>https://cursor.com/blog/agent-swarm-model-economics</guid><source>HackerNews AI</source><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 02:06:13 +0800</pubDate><category>Agent框架</category><category>多Agent</category><category>经济学</category></item><item><title>BAIR 博客：智能免费时代需要为 Agent 设计数据系统</title><link>http://bair.berkeley.edu/blog/2026/07/07/intelligence-is-free-now-what/</link><description>BAIR 博客提出智能免费时代，需要为 AI Agent 设计全新的数据系统，实现由 Agent 管理、为 Agent 服务的数据架构。（来源：BAIR Blog）</description><guid>http://bair.berkeley.edu/blog/2026/07/07/intelligence-is-free-now-what/</guid><source>BAIR Blog</source><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 17:00:00 +0800</pubDate><category>论文与研究</category><category>Agent</category><category>数据系统</category></item><item><title>社区开发者微调 MiniCPM5-1B 打造 657MB 本地思考模型</title><link>https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/07/19/someone-fine-tuned-openbmbs-minicpm5-1b-on-claude-fable-5-traces-to-ship-a-657mb-local-thinking-model/</link><description>社区开发者微调 OpenBMB 的 MiniCPM5-1B 模型，基于 Claude Fable 5 轨迹，打造仅 657MB 的本地思考模型，可完全离线运行。（来源：MarkTechPost）</description><guid>https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/07/19/someone-fine-tuned-openbmbs-minicpm5-1b-on-claude-fable-5-traces-to-ship-a-657mb-local-thinking-model/</guid><source>MarkTechPost</source><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 09:56:50 +0800</pubDate><category>产品与发布</category><category>本地模型</category><category>思考模型</category></item><item><title>控制 LLM 推理努力程度的技术分析</title><link>https://magazine.sebastianraschka.com/p/controlling-reasoning-effort-in-llms</link><description>Sebastian Raschka 深入分析控制 LLM 推理努力程度的方法，包括预算强制和自适应策略，为开发者提供实用指导。（来源：Ahead of AI）</description><guid>https://magazine.sebastianraschka.com/p/controlling-reasoning-effort-in-llms</guid><source>Ahead of AI</source><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 19:16:09 +0800</pubDate><category>论文与研究</category><category>推理</category><category>LLM</category></item><item><title>AWS 与 NVIDIA 推出 NeMo Agent Toolkit 构建专用 Agent 工作流</title><link>https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/machine-learning/build-specialized-agent-workflows-for-your-business-with-amazon-quick-and-nvidia-nemo-agent-toolkit/</link><description>AWS 与 NVIDIA 推出 NeMo Agent Toolkit，结合 Amazon Quick 帮助企业构建专用 Agent 工作流，加速业务自动化。（来源：AWS ML Blog）</description><guid>https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/machine-learning/build-specialized-agent-workflows-for-your-business-with-amazon-quick-and-nvidia-nemo-agent-toolkit/</guid><source>AWS ML Blog</source><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 01:01:32 +0800</pubDate><category>产品与发布</category><category>Agent工作流</category><category>NVIDIA</category></item><item><title>MIT Tech Review：中国 AI 模型引发特朗普 AI 世界内部争论</title><link>https://www.technologyreview.com/2026/07/20/1140675/chinas-ai-models-have-trumps-ai-world-at-war-with-itself/</link><description>MIT Tech Review 分析中国 AI 模型引发特朗普 AI 世界内部争论，各方立场分裂，地缘政治影响加剧。（来源：MIT Tech Review）</description><guid>https://www.technologyreview.com/2026/07/20/1140675/chinas-ai-models-have-trumps-ai-world-at-war-with-itself/</guid><source>MIT Tech Review</source><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 02:00:00 +0800</pubDate><category>行业动态</category><category>地缘政治</category><category>模型竞争</category></item><item><title>使用本地编码代理的实践指南</title><link>https://magazine.sebastianraschka.com/p/using-local-coding-agents</link><description>Sebastian Raschka 分享使用本地编码代理的实践，包括工具选择和工作流配置，帮助开发者高效搭建本地 Agent 环境。（来源：Ahead of AI）</description><guid>https://magazine.sebastianraschka.com/p/using-local-coding-agents</guid><source>Ahead of AI</source><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 19:21:58 +0800</pubDate><category>Agent框架</category><category>本地</category><category>编码代理</category></item><item><title>Simon Willison：编码代理使逆向工程变得廉价</title><link>https://simonwillison.net/2026/Jul/20/cheap-reverse-engineering/#atom-everything</link><description>Simon Willison 指出编码代理使逆向工程变得廉价，越来越多的人用 AI 代理快速逆向软件，成本大幅降低。（来源：Simon Willison）</description><guid>https://simonwillison.net/2026/Jul/20/cheap-reverse-engineering/#atom-everything</guid><source>Simon Willison</source><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 03:24:05 +0800</pubDate><category>Agent框架</category><category>逆向工程</category><category>编码代理</category></item><item><title>索尼再次起诉 AI 音乐生成器 Udio，列出 3 万首侵权歌曲</title><link>https://www.theverge.com/tech/968375/sony-udio-lawsuit-songs-ai-copyright</link><description>索尼音乐娱乐再次起诉 AI 音乐生成器 Udio，列出 3 万首涉嫌侵权的歌曲，AI 版权争议持续升级。（来源：The Verge）</description><guid>https://www.theverge.com/tech/968375/sony-udio-lawsuit-songs-ai-copyright</guid><source>The Verge AI</source><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 06:19:12 +0800</pubDate><category>行业动态</category><category>版权</category><category>诉讼</category></item><item><title>不同模型厂采用同一家 Agentic Infra，AGI 基础设施浮现</title><link>https://www.qbitai.com/2026/07/455805.html</link><description>量子位报道多家模型厂商采用同一家 Agentic Infra，AGI 时代的基础设施逐渐成型，成为行业共同选择。（来源：量子位）</description><guid>https://www.qbitai.com/2026/07/455805.html</guid><source>量子位</source><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 18:33:23 +0800</pubDate><category>Agent框架</category><category>基础设施</category></item><item><title>RESOURCE2SKILL：从多模态资源提取可执行 Agent 技能</title><link>https://x.com/_akhaliq/status/2079238201235927082</link><description>RESOURCE2SKILL 论文提出从人类创建的多模态资源中蒸馏可执行的 Agent 技能，推动 Agent 能力自动化构建。（来源：Twitter @_akhaliq）</description><guid>https://x.com/_akhaliq/status/2079238201235927082</guid><source>Twitter @_akhaliq</source><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 00:13:12 +0800</pubDate><category>论文与研究</category><category>Agent技能</category><category>多模态</category></item><item><title>优化 RAG 系统：分块、检索与贝叶斯搜索降低延迟 40%</title><link>https://dev.to/imus_d7584cbc8ee9b0336256/optimizing-rag-at-scale-chunking-retrieval-and-the-bayesian-search-that-cut-latency-40-2fd1</link><description>DEV.to 文章介绍优化 RAG 系统的方法，包括分块、检索和贝叶斯搜索，成功将延迟降低 40%，